{"tid":558512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港不如淘汰所有雙層巴士，全面改用單層巴士","createTime":"2018-02-12T10:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T10:44:32.000Z","uid":165746,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84fdbaa38e6b78a043782a13a936f74ad638d1f4","tid":558512,"uid":165746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"雙層巴士重心太高，轉彎快少少都有機會翻。再加上翻既時候上層既衝擊力會特別大，所以每次翻車傷亡會特別慘重。近十幾年既個案已經係咩。為安全起見我認為香港淘汰所有雙層巴士，全面改用單層巴士會更好。咁樣有助減輕每次意外既嚴重性同傷亡情況。要滿足乘客需求既話巴士公司可以加密班次來應對"},{"pid":"8d3172c1421fc8588358c4c6ca810037a0af626b","tid":558512,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"淘汰晒班10年駕駛經驗以下既pt司機先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553af50480c0c7fb4bd214193b147dd83d972db1","tid":558512,"uid":137551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"加密班次嘅話條路根本負荷唔到<br />\n一定塞"},{"pid":"3cb869995b6fda4169cb4c9ac3b72c51de20bb73","tid":558512,"uid":51485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:42:57.000Z","msg":"單層又炒車既話 係咪要取消巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72401075f8423803c8929f80cd2db9c9e524d83c","tid":558512,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"無可能<br />\n其實減速就可以"},{"pid":"841e3c3ad5330def104865ece903c837d64d2791","tid":558512,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"都時日日等唔到車加塞車你又屌"},{"pid":"369a34e1ed2790cff94abc837a1acd672597cca9","tid":558512,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72401075f8423803c8929f80cd2db9c9e524d83c","tid":558512,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"無可能<br />\n其實減速就可以"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"最快行50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}